<p>本文作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meltyland-nightmare" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6167306); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6167306&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608342946" alt="Meltyland Nightmare" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6167306)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meltyland-nightmare" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6167306); return false;">Meltyland Nightmare</a></span><br />
<a href="/erwin-schrodinger-s-personnel-files">首席研究员祖绫的人事页。</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
